{"questionId":"12930","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Let <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"z = a + b{\\text{i}}\">\n  <mi>z</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mi>a</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mi>b</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>i</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>, <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"a\">\n  <mi>a</mi>\n</math></span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\text{b}} \\in {\\mathbb{R}^ + }\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>b</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>∈</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mrow>\n        <mi mathvariant=\"double-struck\">R</mi>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span> and let&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\text{arg}}\\,z = \\theta \">\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>arg</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>z</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mi>θ</mi>\n</math></span>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Find an expression in terms of <em>θ</em> for&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\text{arg}}\\left( {z - 2a} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>arg</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>z</mi>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n      <mi>a</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\pi&nbsp; - \\theta \">\n  <mi>π</mi>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mi>θ</mi>\n</math></span>&nbsp;(or any equivalent) &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[1 mark]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"12930","referenceCode":"19M.2.AHL.TZ1.H_6b.i","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"Find an expression in terms of θ for arg ( z − 2 a ) .","paper":"